[~shishir.roy] This provides a little more info, seems there's a threading issue:
{code}
Microsoft C++ exception: Platform::WrongThreadException
{code}

Do you know what Titanium methods your application is calling when the crash occurs (i.e: Titanium.Netowork.*)? I'm also curious if this issue occurs for you on 8.1.0.GA or 8.2.0.GA, it looks to be a regression introduced since 8.0.0.GA and knowing which SDK version it does/doesn't occur on would help track it down.

[~shishir.roy] You can test these changes by downloading the latest 8_3_X branch build:

http://builds.appcelerator.com/#8_3_X

or

{code}
appc ti sdk install -b 8_3_X
{code}
